<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Modern Web Experience</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f0f4f8, #d9e2ec);
      border: 1px solid red;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100vh;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 42px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 25px auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #4a4a4a;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-left: 5px solid #2c3e50;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.4s ease;
    }

    p:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    header {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    header nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 12px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    header nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    button {
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9;
      transform: scale(1.07);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ffffff;
     background-color: #2c3e50 ;
      padding: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('head') %>

  <h1>Welcome to Our Modern Web App</h1>
  <p>
    Explore our platform to discover cutting-edge solutions and tools for your digital needs. 
    Built with a robust backend powered by Node.js and Express, combined with MongoDB for seamless data management.
  </p>

  <p>
    Experience the latest trends in responsive design and user-friendly interfaces. 
    Join us as we redefine the standards of web development with modern technologies and intuitive designs.
  </p>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Modern Web Experience. All Rights Reserved.
  </footer>
</body>

</html>
